{"tid":629771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國陸軍徵科學家研發鋼鐵人戰鬥服設計案　2018 進行首批量產","createTime":"2018-04-15T03:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T12:45:13.000Z","uid":53379,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6cbbedaa348f90e0d69448ea77221f2166d99773","tid":629771,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:52:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美國陸軍徵科學家研發鋼鐵人戰鬥服設計案　2018 進行首批量產</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2018-02-13 15:32:51<br />\n    <br />\n張岑宇／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n受到鋼鐵人電影中奈米戰鬥服裝的啟發，美國陸軍正在尋找創新的科學家，為士兵創造未來派新一代戰鬥服的原型設計。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.limitlessiq.com/media/wysiwyg/201802/20180213/39FE8E8B00000578-0-image-a-1_1478111758419.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.limitlessiq.com%2Fmedia%2Fwysiwyg%2F201802%2F20180213%2F39FE8E8B00000578-0-image-a-1_1478111758419.jpg&h=a973808a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲鋼鐵人服將成真！（圖／翻攝自每日郵報，下同）<br />\n<br />\n據《每日郵報》報導，美國特種作戰司令部（SOCOM）在 2017 年12 月份發布一項徵求案，希望各廠商提供「戰術突擊輕量操作服」（Tactical Assault Light Operator Suit）（TALOS），俗稱「鋼鐵人」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.limitlessiq.com/media/wysiwyg/201802/20180213/39FE8E8F00000578-0-image-a-3_1478111788688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.limitlessiq.com%2Fmedia%2Fwysiwyg%2F201802%2F20180213%2F39FE8E8F00000578-0-image-a-3_1478111788688.jpg&h=94053767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新的標案要求戰鬥服必須增加更多高科技技術，像是防彈力等，以及必須提升安全性，還要能夠提升隱密性，為士兵的生命提供更多的安全保障，減少腦損傷危害，以及希望能夠藉此戰鬥服提升作戰能力！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.limitlessiq.com/media/wysiwyg/201802/20180213/39FE8E8300000578-0-image-a-4_1478111796447.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.limitlessiq.com%2Fmedia%2Fwysiwyg%2F201802%2F20180213%2F39FE8E8300000578-0-image-a-4_1478111796447.jpg&h=3221dc54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國特種部隊司令部希望戰鬥服內的電池能夠提供幾千瓦的直流電，並且可以持續數小時，但體積最好可以方便攜帶，背包般的大小是上限。公告明確指出，電源應該低於 120 伏特，不要超過 600 伏特。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.limitlessiq.com/media/wysiwyg/201802/20180213/46C4635300000578-5124123-image-m-138_1511881900787.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.limitlessiq.com%2Fmedia%2Fwysiwyg%2F201802%2F20180213%2F46C4635300000578-5124123-image-m-138_1511881900787.jpg&h=f44deab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實這不是鋼鐵人裝第一次被提出，早在 2013 年 9 月，特種部隊司令部就已經募集設計案，美國從 2015 年開始，就在計畫為特種部隊打造一款能強化移動能力、增加防護程度的裝甲服「Talos」，運用「液態金屬」技術，透過電流及磁場的作用，裝甲可瞬間固化抵禦爆裂物碎片或子彈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.limitlessiq.com/media/wysiwyg/201802/20180213/39FE8E8700000578-0-image-a-2_1478111782735.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.limitlessiq.com%2Fmedia%2Fwysiwyg%2F201802%2F20180213%2F39FE8E8700000578-0-image-a-2_1478111782735.jpg&h=4faa71f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTalos 還在內部配置電機及液壓系統，增強士兵力量、頭盔中也搭載夜視鏡，提供夜戰能力，內部多處設置的感應器可偵測士兵身體狀態，在受傷時甚至會產生「修復泡沫」，協助士兵處理傷口；這款裝甲測試順利的話，會在 2018 年進行第一批量產。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-5309795/US-Army-wants-designs-futuristic-Iron-Man-suit.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fsciencetech%2Farticle-5309795%2FUS-Army-wants-designs-futuristic-Iron-Man-suit.html&d=e2PC5uQKZy0AmFTAHjyWpnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=ab4db427\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-5309795/US-Army-wants-designs-futuristic-Iron-Man-suit.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.limitlessiq.com/news/post/view/id/3607/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.limitlessiq.com%2Fnews%2Fpost%2Fview%2Fid%2F3607%2F&d=e2PC5uQKZy0AmFTAHjyWpnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=26b48c0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.limitlessiq.com/news/post/view/id/3607/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RKcqHaPhkkM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRKcqHaPhkkM&d=e2PC5uQKZy0AmFTAHjyWpnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=6f246450\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RKcqHaPhkkM</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知今年有無機會可以見到"},{"pid":"99b1af7ab05ff61d85b3d25461826147cd9a2b0f","tid":629771,"uid":82640,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:53:33.000Z","msg":"中國整可能會漏電、爆炸、唔夠力..."},{"pid":"eb3d9b9e38617e6a839131b2ffe81856c93e5842","tid":629771,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:55:43.000Z","msg":"halo"},{"pid":"8110479729160187d7bda9bda3aae01dff22f1a1","tid":629771,"uid":39508,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99b1af7ab05ff61d85b3d25461826147cd9a2b0f","tid":629771,"uid":82640,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:53:33.000Z","msg":"中國整可能會漏電、爆炸、唔夠力..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:55:48.000Z","msg":"warning&hellip;warning...high temperaturn...BOOM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac07bb0610fc90b9dc992e6ee187b826a58a6fdd","tid":629771,"uid":39508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:56:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中國整可能會漏電、爆炸、唔夠力...</blockquote>warning&hellip;warning...high <span style=\"color: red;\">temperature</span>...BOOM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a20f460e9457b10892d82511240d5bd11125e55","tid":629771,"uid":94828,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"99b1af7ab05ff61d85b3d25461826147cd9a2b0f","tid":629771,"uid":82640,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:53:33.000Z","msg":"中國整可能會漏電、爆炸、唔夠力..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:57:01.000Z","msg":"自殺式武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73651f3317ece77e0b1fa01e0c7450362687dc3e","tid":629771,"uid":67468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a20f460e9457b10892d82511240d5bd11125e55","tid":629771,"uid":94828,"li